fields.name: Ranked Rashguard - White
fields.description:
These rashguards have been developed with IBJJF guidelines for no-gi grappling competition in mind. Coming in white, blue, purple, brown and black, they are ideal for competing and everyday training.

 

They’re kinda sorta based on football uniforms, which is cool, if you ask me. And we would say that because we designed it that way. So there.

 

Made with turbo high quality materials, and even a little rubber strip on the inside waistband to stop your gut from flipping out when you’re doing a berimbolo or whatever.

fields.name: Athlete Gi - White
fields.description: Our Athlete is one of our most popular gis, and for good reason. A perfect balance of form and function, the Athlete is our all-rounder. Sturdy enough for daily training but fancy enough to literally melt your training partners’ eyeballs, this special edition kimono uses Ecru fabric. Ecru is a really fancy name for “unbleached” and is popular with purists since it harkens back to the good old days when stuff wasn’t bleached. Now everything is bleached. But not in the old days. And not this gi!

fields.name: Standard Gi - White
fields.description:
The Base-K is the culmination of almost 12 years in the jiujitsu industry. A clean, refined look, that is understated and allows you to customise your gi as much or as little as you want. The Scramble logo, after over a decade in the sport, now really stands for something, which is why we limited the decorations to a few simple instances of the logo itself.

 

The lack of unnecessary decorations meant we were able to keep the price lower than our other flagship gis and maintain the focus on quality.

 

The materials, fit and finish speak for themselves.

The trousers have our SK (Scramble Kimono) logo embroidered directly.

fields.name: Grey Tee
fields.description:
Our collaboration with the living legend that is Kazushi Sakuraba, arguably the greatest MMA fighter of all time. This design features an exploded diagram of the nervous system of the human body, a nod to the “vale tudo” (anything goes) rule set of early MMA, and Sakuraba’s all-round ability to attack any part of the human body with creativity and skill.

 

Soft and comfortable materials and high quality finishings feature throughout.

fields.name: Jacket - Navy
fields.description:
Lightweight rain jacket
Highly water-resistant
Imanari wore it, so you better get it.

 

Superior construction, fit and feel. This lightweight rain jacket has an excellent water-resistant nylon construction and coating, including waterproof zippers, and a lightweight mesh liner. An elastic waistband allows you to cinch the jacket if necessary, as do velcro cuffs. The jacket is navy blue and finished with reflective print Scramble logo hits for nighttime adventures.

fields.name: SWIFTY BALANCE BOARD - CLASSIC
fields.description:
Feel like a surfer!

 

Using a balance board can improve your balance, agility and core body strength in the comfort of your home. It works by destabilising your lower body which activates muscles in your feet and ankles and up into your legs, hips and core. Using a balance board activates synapses in your brain which helps to improve balance and muscle coordination, it’s a lot of fun to use!

 

• Indoor balance-training device and unique storage solution
• 'Classic’ balance boards feature four fins which provide extra control
• ‘Fishtail’ balance boards feature no fins for advanced balance boarding
• Large 150mm diameter 100% natural cork roller
• Plywood treated with plant-based pigment and clear varnish
• Designed and made in Manchester UK at SwiftyHQ

fields.name: SWIFTY FITNESS RESISTANCE BANDS
fields.description:
The Swifty Fitness resistance bands fit seamlessly into your workout routine, adapting to multiple fitness levels. The bands offer variable resistance - use them for a range of exercises to increase muscular endurance, strength and flexibility.

 

• Varying strengths
• Travel friendly
• Perfect for toning
• Challenge multiple muscle groups

fields.description:
Lightweight waffle effect gym towel

120cm x 60cm

Looks amazing

Soaks up all nearby liquids aggressively and effectively.

fields.name: SCRAMBLE ‘YUBI’ BJJ FINGER TAPE
fields.description: This finger tape is designed for us in jiu jitsu, judo and other grappling arts. Provides extra support on sore joints. 1.25cm x 10m
